Package es.csic.iiia.nsm.norm.generation.cbr

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Case
    A case of a Case Base.
    CaseBase
    A case base is a base of CBR cases.
    CaseDescription
    A case description, containing the conflict source (which is a transition of views for consecutive time steps) and the conflict itself (at time t=0)
    CaseSolution
    A case solution is a solution aimed to solve a conflicting situation described in the CaseDescription of a Case.
    CBRNormGenerationMachine
    A norm generation machine that uses Case Based Reasoning (CBR) to generates norms from conflicts.
